# 🚀 Advanced AI Ticketing System

## 📌 Project Overview

The Advanced AI Ticketing System is a smart internal support platform
that automates ticket handling using AI. It analyzes incoming tickets,
decides whether they can be auto-resolved, and if not, intelligently
assigns them.

## 🎯 Problem Statement

-   Manual ticket handling causes delays
-   Incorrect routing
-   High workload

## 🧠 Key Features

1.  AI Ticket Analysis
2.  Auto Resolution
3.  Intelligent Assignment
4.  Ticket Lifecycle
5.  Analytics Dashboard

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

-   FastAPI
-   SQLite
-   Python

## ⚙️ Setup

pip install -r requirements.txt\
python -m uvicorn main:app --reload

## 🧪 APIs

POST /ticket\
PUT /ticket/{ticket_id}/status\
GET /analytics

## ⚠️ Limitations

-   No frontend
-   Rule-based AI

## 🚀 Future Improvements

-   Add LLM
-   Add frontend
-   Better analytics

